# No configuration required — pair the app by scanning the QR code from the
# Terra dashboard's streaming page (Pair tab in the app). The reusable rt.
# token in the QR carries everything, stored in the device keychain.

# Optional, development only: pre-fill the (public, username-like) dev-id so
# the producer flow works before the first scan.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_TERRA_DEV_ID=your-dev-id
